Distribution . Most parts of Europe (except the northernmost regions, but including southern Sweden and the Caucasus Major), Turkey , Transcaucasia ( Armenia , Azerbaijan ), Israel , Iran , Turkmenistan , western Siberia ( Lindroth 1992 ;
Kryzhanovskij et al . 1995
; Bousquet 2017 ). We record it for the first time from Israel .

